name: Quasar-wind-grid
tagline: Repository of grid results for the 2015 Quasar wind models
body:
### Grid of QSO Wind Models

This page contains information of how to access spectrum output files for a grid of QSO wind models run for the Matthews et al. 2015 paper. The grids of output files can be downloaded by clicking the zip or tar.gz buttons above.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
